hadiths[49]{hadithnumber,text}:
3855,"Hazrat Usama bin shareek (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha ( to dekha ke) aap ke Sahaba (aap ki majlis mein) aisey bethey they goya unke saron par perindey hon, (yani intehai ba-adab aur pursukoon they ( chunanche maine salam kya aur beth gaya. idhar-udhar se badwi log aaye aur unhoney puchha ke aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya ham dawa daaru kar liya keren? aapney farmaya : '' dawaa kya karo, bila-shuba Allah azz-w-jall ne koi bimari paida nahin ki magar uski dawa bhi paida ki hai, siwaye eik bimari ke yani budhapa (us ka koi ilaj nahin.'' ("
3856,Hazrat Umme-Munzir (Salma) binte-Qais Ansariya (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey ghar tashrif laye aap ke sath Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they jo bimari se uthey they aur kamzor they. hamarey yahan khajuron ke khoshay latak rahey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uthey aur un se khaney lagey aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi khaney ke liye uthey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se farmaya : '' ruk jao ! tum abhi kamzor ho.'' chunanche Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) khaney sey) rukey rahey . Umme- munzir kehti hain ke maine jo aur chuqandar pakaaey aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiye to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Ali ! lo ye tumharey liye mufeed hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : ( merey Shekh ( Harun (bin Abdullah ( ne ( apney Shekh ( Abu-Dawud se Umme- munzir ke baarey mein naqal kya ke ye '' adwiya '' ( bano Adi ki khatoon ( hain.
3857,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' tumhari dawaaon mein jin se tum ilaj kartey ho agar koi behtar dawa hai to ( un mein se eik ( seengi lagwaana hai.''"
3858,"Hazrat Salma (Raziallahu anha) ( zauja abu-Raafe (Raziallahu anhu)) jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khaadima thin , bayan karti hain ke jo koi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas sar dard ki shikayat lekar aata to aap usey farmatey : '' seengi lagwaao '' aur jo koi paon ke dard ki takleef batata to aap farmatey : '' mahndii lagao .''"
3859,Hazrat abu-Kabsha Anmaari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi akram (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney sar ke baalai (upri) hissey aur dono kandhon ke darmiyan seengi lagwaaya kartey they aur farmatey they : ''jis kisi ne un maqamat se khoon ke kuch hissey baha diye to wo kisi bimari ke liye koi aur dawaa na bhi ley to usey koi zarar nahin pahunchega.''
3860,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen martaba seengi lagwaai gardan ki dono janib ki ragon par aur kandhon ke darmiyan ( kamar ke ooper shuru mein . Maamer kehtey hain : maine seengi lagwa li to mera hafiza jata raha yahan tak ke mujhey Namaz mein Fatiha padhney mein bhi luqma diya jata tha. unhoney apni khopdi par) ghalat jagah par) seengi lagwaai thi.
3861,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs sattarah , Unais aur ikkees taareekh ( qamrii ( ko seengi lagwaaey usey her bimari se shifa hogi .''"
3862,"Hazrat Keesa binte-abi Bakrah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unke walid Hazrat abu-Bakra (Raziallahu anhu) mangal ke roz seengi lagwaaney se mana kya kartey they. unka khayal tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : '' mangal ka din khoon ka din hai, us main eik ghadi aisi aati hai ke us mein khoon nahin rukta.''"
3863,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dard ki wajeh se apni peeth par seengi lagwaai thi.
3864,Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf eik muaalij bheja jisney unki rag kaati.
3865,"Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne daaghney se mana farmaya hai, pas ham ne dagh lagwaaey magar ye kaamyab rahey na mufeed Sabit huey. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat imran malaaika ka salam suna kartey they. jab unhoney dagh lagwaaey to ye silsila munqata ho gaya. phir jab chhod diya to phir se salam sunney lagey ."
3866,"Hazrat Jabir (bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma)) se manqul hai ke Hazrat Saad bin Muaz ko teer lagney ke baais jo zakhm aaya tha, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko dagh lagwaaya tha."
3867,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne naak mein dawa dali thi.
3868,Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se nashrah ke mutalliq puchha gaya to aapney farmaya : ''ye shetani amal hai.''
3869,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko suna, aap farmatey they : ''mujhey koi parwa nahin jo chahey karta phirun agar main tiryaaq piyun ya mankey latkaaun ya apni taraf se she'r kahun . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke tiryaq ka istimal na karna Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khususiyat thi. aur tiryaaq ke istimal mein ulama ki eik jamaat ne rukhsat di hai."
3870,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khabees dawaaon ke istimal se mana farmaya hai.
3871,Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke eik muaalij ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se maindak ke mutalliq puchha ke kya usey dawaa mein dal liya karey to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us ( tabeeb ( ko maindak ke qatl kerney se mana kar diya.
3872,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney zahar piya ( to aakhirat mein) uska zahar uskey haath mein hoga jisey wo jahannam ki aag mein hamesha hamesha-hamesha tak peeta rahega .''
3873,"Hazrat Tariq bin Suwed ya Suwed bin Tariq (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sharab ke mutalliq puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mana farmaya , usney phir sawal kya to aapney mana farmaya , to usney kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! ye dawaa hai. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' nahin ye bimari hai.''"
3874,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bila-shuba Allah taala ne bimari utaari hai to dawa bhi nazil farmaai hai aur her bimari ke liye dawa hai, lihaza dawa istimal kya karo lekin haram se ilaj na karo.''"
3875,"Hazrat Saad (bin abi Waqas ( (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main bahut sakht bimar ho gaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) meri iyaadat ke liye tashrif laye . aapney apna dast-mubarak meri chhaati ke darmiyan rakha , yahan tak ke maine uski thandak apney dil mein mehsoos ki. to aapney farmaya : ''tum dil ke mareez ho, bano Saqeef ke Haris bin Kalda ke paas jao, wo tabaabat karta hai, usey chahiye ke Madina ki ajwa khajuron mein se saat khajuren lekar unhen guthliyon samet koot ley aur phir tumhen khila dey.''"
3876,"Janab Aamir bin Saad abi Waqas apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs subh ko ajwa khajoor ke saat daney kha ley usey us din koi zahar ya jadu nuqsan nahin dega .''"
3877,"Hazrat umme-Qais binte-Mohsin (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke main apney bete ko lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui .) chunkey uskey halaq mein takleef thi to ( maine uskey latkey huey galey ungli se ooper kiye they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tum apney bachon ke galey latakney ka ilaj ungli se kyon karti ho? aud hindi ikhtiyar kar lo, us mein saat bimariyon ki shifa hai. un mein se eik '' zaatul janb'' ( pehlu ka dard bhi) hai) jis mein ye mufeed hai) halaq ki takleef mein usey naak mein tapkaya jata hai aur pehlu ke dard mein pani ke sath khilaya jata hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke aud se murad qust hai."
3878,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' kapdey safed pehna karo, ye tumharey sab libaason mein behtar libas hai. usi main apni maiyaton ko kafan diya karo aur tumharey surmon mein se behtareen surma Asmad hai jo beenai ko tez karta aur palkon ke baal ugata hai.''"
3879,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bayan kya, aapney farmaya : '' nazar lag jana haq hai.''"
3880,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jis shakhs ki nazar lagti usey hukm diya jata tha ke wuzu karkey ( wuzu ka pani ( dey , phir us se bimar ko) jisey nazar lagi ho ( ghusl karaya jata tha."
3881,"Hazrat Asma bint Yazid bin Sakan (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahey they : '' apni auladon ko chhipey tareeqey se qatl mat karo . bila-shuba doodh peeney ke dinon mein aurat se mubashrat ka asar ye hota hai ke bacha (bada ho kar jab ghud sawari karta hai to ( ghodey se gir jata hai.''"
3882,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) , Hazrat Judama Asadiya (Raziallahu anha) se bayan karti hain, unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : '' mera irada hua ke doodh pilaney ke dinon mein mubashrat se mana kar dun magar mujhey yaad dilaaya gaya ke Romi aur Farsi log aisa kartey hain magar unke bachon ko koi nuqsan nahin hota hai. Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : ghaila ye hai ke jis zamaney mein aurat bachey ko doodh pilati ho uska shohar us se mubashrat karey."
3883,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''dam-jhaad , gandey mankey aur jadu ki chizen ya tehreeren shirk hain.'' unki ehliya ne kaha : aap ye kyon kar kehtey hain? Allah ki qasam ! meri aankh dard ki wajeh se goya nikli jati thi to main falan yahudi ke paas jati aur wo mujhey dam karta tha. jab wo dam karta to mera dard ruk jata tha. Hazrat Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ye shaitan ki kaaristaani hoti thi. wo teri aankh main apni ungli maarta tha, to jab wo (yahudi) dam karta to (shaitan) baaz aa jata tha. halanke tujhey yehi kuchh kehna kafi tha jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kaha kartey they (أذهب الباس رب الناس ، اشف أنت الشافي ، لا شفاء إلا شفاؤك ، شفاء لا يغادر سقما) ''aey logon ke Rab ! dukh door kar dey , shifa inayat farma , to hi shifa deney wala hai, teri shifa ke siwa kahin koi shifa nahin, aisi shifa inayat farma jo koi dukh baqi na rehney dey.''"
3884,Hazrat Imran bin Husain (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dum jhaad sirf nazare bad mein hai ya zahreeley dank mein.''
3885,"Janab Yusuf bin Muhammad ya Muhammad bin Yusuf bin Sabit bin Qais bin Shamaas apney walid se wo unke dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hazrat Sabit bin Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan aaye . . . Ahmed ne kaha : jabkey wo mareez they. . . to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne dua farmaee (اكشف الباس رب الناس ، عن ثابت بن Qais بن شماس) ''aey logon ke paalney waley ! us takleef ko Sabit bin Qais bin shamaas se door farma dey.'' phir aapney wadi Bat'haan ki mitti li , usey eik piyaley mein dala , phir us par pani phunk kar dala aur phir usey us par chhidak diya. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : Ibne Sarah ne raawi ka naam Yusuf bin Muhammad zikr kiya hai aur yehi sahih hai."
3886,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke ham jahiliyat mein dam jhaad kiya kartey they to ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap ka is baarey mein kya khayal hai? aapney farmaya : ''apney dam mujhey batao, dam karney mein koi harj nahin ba-sharte-ke shirk na ho.''"
3887,Hazrat Shifaa binte Abdulla (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey yahan tashrif laye jabkey main Ummul-momenin Hazrat Hafsa (Raziallahu anha) ke paas thi to aapney mujh se farmaya : ''tum is namla (bachchon ki pasliyon par nikalney wali phunsiyon) ka dam kyon nahin sikha deti ho jaisey ke isey likhna sikhaya hai.
3888,"Janab Sehal bin Hanif (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke ham eik nadi ke paas se guzrey to main us mein dakhil ho gaya aur ghusl kiya. bahir nikla to bukhar chadha hua tha. ye baat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko batai gaee to aapney farmaya : '' Abu-Saabit ko kaho ke isey dam kar dey.'' (Rubaab kehti hai) ke maine (Sehal bin Haneef sey) arz kiya : aaqa ! kya dam mufeed hotey hain? farmaya : ''dam bad-nazari , saanp ke kaatey aur bichhu ke dank hi mein mufeed hotey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : (الحمة) ka lafz saanp aur her dasney waley moozi janwar par bola jata hai."
3889,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dam in chizon hi se hota hai bad-nazari , zahreeley janwer ke dank aur behtey khoon se.'' Abbas (Anbari) ne ''bad-nazari'' ka zikr nahin kiya. aur is hadees ke alfaz Sulaiman bin Dawud ke hain."
3890,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne Janab Sabit Bunani se kaha : kya main tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka (sikhaya hua) dam na karun? unhoney kaha : kyon nahin. to unhoney kaha :(اللهم ! رب الناس ، مذهب الباس ، اشف أنت الشافي ، لا شافي إلا أنت اشفه شفاء لا يغادر سقما) ''aey Allah ! logon ke paalney waley, dukhon ke door kerney waley ! shifa inayat farma , to hi Shaafi hai, terey siwa koi shifa nahin dey sakta , isey shifa dey aisi shifa jo koi bimari na rehney dey.''"
3891,"Hazrat Usman bin Abi Al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua jabke mujhey bada sakht dard ho raha tha, qarib tha ke mujhey halak kar dey. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''dard ki jagah par saat baar apna dahina haath phero aur yun kaho (أعوذ بعزة الله وقدرته من شر أجد) ''main Allah ki izzat aur qudrat ki panah chahta hun is takleef se jis mein main mubtala hun.'' chunanche maine aisey hi kiya tu Allah ne meri takleef door kar di. tab se main apney ghar walon aur doosron ko ye dam batata aa raha hun."
3892,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''tum mein se jis ko koi takleef ho jaey ya uska bhai bimar ho jaey to usey yun dam karey (ربنا الله الذي في السماء ‘ تقدس اسمك ‘ أمرك في السماء والأرض ‘ رحمتك في السماء فاجعل رحمتك في الأرض ‘ اغفر لنا حوبنا وخطايانا أنت ‘ رب الطيبين ‘ أنزل رحمة من رحمتك ‘ وشفاء من شفائك على هذا الوجع) ''hamara Rab Allah hai jo aasman mein hai. (aey Allah !) tera naam muqaddas hai, aasman aur zameen mein tera hukm nafiz (lagoo) hai, teri rehmat jis tarah aasman mein (aam) hai zameen mein bhi (aam) kar dey, hamarey gunah aur khataeyn maaf kar dey, to paak logon ka Rab hai, apni rehmat aur shifa ka eik hissey is bimari par nazil farma dey.'' to wo shifa pa jaeyga."
3893,"Janab Amr bin Shuaib apney walid se wo apney dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) dar ya ghabrahat ke moqe par unhen ye kalmaat sikhaya kartey they (أعوذ بكلمات الله التامة من غضبه وشر عباده ومن همزات الشياطين وأن يحضرون) ''main Allah ke kamil kalimaat ki panah mein aata hun, uski narazi sey, uskey bandon ki shararaton sey, shaitanon ke waswason se aur is baat se ke wo merey paas ayen.'' chunanche Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) apney samajhdaar bachchon ko ye kalimaat sikha diya kartey they aur jo nasamajh hotey , unhen likh kar unke galey mein dal detey."
3894,Janab Yazid bin Abu-Ubaid kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Salma (bin Akwa) (Raziallahu anhu) ki pindli par talwaar lagney ka nishan dekha. maine puchha ke ye kaisa nishan hai? to unhoney bataya ke ye mujhey khaibar ke roz lagi thi aur log kehney lagey ke Salma to gaya ! to mujhey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas laya gaya. aapney mujh par teen baar phunk maari (jis mein halka sa luaab dahan bhi tha) to uskey baad se ab tak mujhey iski koi takleef nahin hui.
3895,"Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke jab koi shakhs bimar ho jata to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apna luaab letey , phir usey mitti lagatey aur yun farmatey (تربة أرضنا بريقة بعضنا يشفى سقيمنا بإذن ربنا) ''mitti hamari zameen ki, hamarey eik ke luaab ke sath , shifa paey hamara mareez , hamarey Rab ke hukm se.''"
3896,"Janab khaarija bin Salat Tameemi apney chacha (Ilaaqa bin Sihaar Saleeti Tameemi (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur Islam qubul kiya. phir wapis lotey to eik qom ke paas se guzrey , unke yahan eik majnun aadmi tha jo zanjeeron mein jakdaa hua tha. uskey ghar walon ne un se kaha : tehqiq hamein khabar mili hai ke tumhara ye sahab ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( khair ke sath aaya hai. to kya tumharey paas koi chiz hai jis se tum iska ilaj kar do? chunanche maine usko Sura-Faatiha se dam kiya to wo theek ho gaya. phir unhoney mujhey so bakriyan deen to main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap ko khabar di. aapney puchha : ''kya bas yehi?'' Musaddad ne doosrey moqe par kaha : ''kya tum ne iskey alawa bhi kuchh padha tha?'' maine kaha : nahin. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ley lo. qasam meri umr ki ! log batil dam, jhaad se khatey hain, jabkey tum aisey dam se kha rahey ho jo haq hai.''"
3897,Janab Khaarija bin Salat apney chacha (Hazrat Ilaaqa bin Sihaar Saleeti (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke wo eik qom ke paas se guzrey (aur eik mareez ko) teen din tak subah aur shaam Sura- Fatiha se dam kartey rahey. jab wo usey puri padh letey to apna luaab jama karkey mareez par phunk detey. is se wo goya apney bandhan se khul gaya. is par un logon ne unko kuchh maal diya to wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey . . . aur phir mazkura baala hadees Musaddad ki manind riwayat ki.
3898,"Janab Suhel bin Abu-Saaleh apney walid se riwayat kartey hain, wo kehtey hain ke maine qabeela Aslam ke eik shakhs se suna, usney bayan kiya ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas baitha hua tha ke aap ke Sahaba mein se eik sahabi aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aaj raat dank lagney ki wajeh se main subh tak so nahin saka hun. aapney puchha : ''kya tha ?'' usney bataya ke bichchhoo tha. aapney farmaya : ''agar tum shaam ke waqt ye dua padh letey (أعوذ بكلمات الله التامات من شر ما خلق) ''main Allah ke kamil kalimaat ke sath panah leta hun har us chiz ke shar se jo usney paida farmaee hai.'' to tumhen In-Sha-Allah koi nuksan na pahunchta."
3899,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik shakhs laya gaya jisey bichchhoo ne dank maara tha. aapney farmaya : ''agar isney (أعوذ بكلمات الله التامة من شر ما خلق) ke kalimaat padhey hotey to isey dank na lagta'' ya farmaya : ''isey dukh na pahunchta.'' (is dua ka maani ooper zikr ho chuka hai.)
3900,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke as-haabe Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka eik giroh eik safar mein tha ke unhoney eik arab qabeele ke paas padaaw kiya. un logon mein se kisi ne kaha : hamarey sardar ko kisi chiz ne das liya hai to tum mein se kisi ke paas koi cheez hai jo hamarey is aadmi ke liye mufeed ho? Sahaba mein se kisi eik ne kaha : haan , Allah ki qasam ! main dam kiya karta hun, lekin baat ye hai ke ham ne tum logon se mehmani talab ki thi to tum ne inkar kar diya tha. so mein bhi dam nahin karunga yahan tak ke tum mujhey iska iwaz (badal) do. chunanche unhoney bakriyon ka eik rewad dena tasleem kiya, to wo uskey paas gaey aur us par Sura-Faatiha se dam kiya. is beech mein wo us par luaab bhi phoonktey jatey they yahan tak ke wo theek ho gaya goya ke bandhan se khul gaya ho. chunanche un logon ne iwazaana jo tey kiya tha purey ka pura dey diya, to sathiyon ne kaha : isey aapas mein taqseem kar lo. magar dam kerney waley ne kaha : nahin, taqseem mat karo yahan tak ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchengey aur aap se mashwara karengey. chunanche wo agli subah Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas hazir huey aur sara qissa bayan kiya. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''tumhen kahan se khabar mili thi ke ye dam hai? tum ne khoob kiya, unhen aapas mein taqseem kar lo aur mera hissey bhi rakho.''"
3901,"Janab Khaarija bin Salat Tameemi apney chacha se riwayat kartey hain ke ham log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas se rawana huey aur eik arab qabeela ke yahan padaaw kiya. unhoney kaha : tehqiq hamen khabar mili hai ke tum us aadmi ke paas se koi khair lekar aaye ho, to kya tumharey paas koi dawaa ya dam hai ke hamarey yahan eik majnun hai jo zanjeeron mein jakdaa hua hai? ham ne kaha : haan . chunanche wo us majnun ko jo zanjeeron mein jakdaa hua tha ley aaye . main us par teen roz tak subah, shaam Sura-Faatiha padhta raha . jab main surat mukammal karta , to apna luaab jama karta aur us par phunk deta tha. usney kaha : phir goya ke wo apney bandhan se khul gaya. aur unhoney mujhey uska iwazaana (badal) diya. maine kaha : nahin, yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se daryaft kar lun. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kha lo. meri umr ki qasam ! log to batil damon ka iwaz khatey hain aur tum haq dam ka badal kha rahey ho.''"
3902,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab bimar ho jatey to muawwizaat (قل هو الله أحد ، قل أعوذ برب الفلق) aur (قل أعوذ برب الناس) padh kar apney ooper phunk letey they. phir jab aap ki takleef badh gaee to main unhen aap par padhti aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka haath pakad kar aap ke jism par pherti is umeed se ke in mein barkat hai.
3903,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke meri walida ne chaha ke main qadrey moti ho jaun taake mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ghar bheja ja sakey. magar mujhey unki hasabe-mansha kisi chiz se fayda na hua yahan tak ke unhoney mujhey kakdi aur khajoor mila kar khilaai to us se main khoob moti tazi ho gaee.
